{"tid":635351,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你會推一個無辜嘅人落樓嗎？？","createTime":"2018-04-20T05:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T15:27:12.000Z","uid":86509,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac0aedf01787d5ec9eb1047e50a1ee94847bc95","tid":635351,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:10:37.000Z","msg":"Derren Brown: Pushed to the Edge<br />\n<br />\n這期節目通過實驗，對「社會屈從性」進行了一次深入的探討。實驗中，達倫布朗試圖讓一個叫克里斯的男子，在72分鐘之內完成將一位陌生人從高樓推下去的謀殺決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av20374883/?redirectFrom=h5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav20374883%2F%3FredirectFrom%3Dh5&d=wFUHqL6JyT4V6SMNQ0yoBv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=24918570\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av20374883/?redirectFrom=h5</a><br />\n有啲電話會自動跳去m 版有可能有6分鐘限制，自己校網頁版啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係超好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家點睇呢個節目？？<br />\n當中個魔術師講大部份人都會推又係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對比返以前着名嘅米爾葛籣實驗，我覺得其實所言非虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1666df5bd4d27f041db79960c947ebf0ed75c7","tid":635351,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"之前開錯咗時事台靜到，<br />\n唔知呢邊會唔會多啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c731d0aae5807ba4d8899639ca5328343b04012","tid":635351,"uid":86509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"再冇人回我就推自己落樓算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26cd7cc2a1d403f5b334b6fd5afd17c498c2404","tid":635351,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"此post已完<br />\n樓主已跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /